column4: whenever I attempt to execute firefox 1.5.2 I get this error http://pastebin.com/678447

ok, but those messages aren't the reason
it's the messages about not finding shared object file that are killing it

use synaptic and try search and see if it finds stuff for pango
whenever you see a message about not finding a shared object, it's talking about a library
